results.responseText:
For an enterprise cost model, the grounded numbers to anchor on are Gemini 3 Flash at $0.10, Gemini 3 Pro at $1.00, plus context caching support in the Gemini 3 family {{fact:ground_truth:GEMINI_3}}.

I would structure the model around 3 scenarios rather than inventing spend totals from incomplete evidence: light production traffic, team-scale embedded usage, and high-throughput platform usage. The key cost levers are model mix (Flash vs. Pro), repeated-context reuse, and the cache hit rate you can sustain. {{fact:ground_truth:GEMINI_3}}

Procurement checklist: confirm the official pricing page as the source of truth, define the routing threshold for when a request escalates from Flash to Pro, and validate caching semantics before committing a standard. {{fact:ground_truth:GEMINI_3}}

